    "description": "The arctic is a <strong>big</strong> place. Ever wanted to explore the endless expanses of the arctic as a Polar Bear? Well now you can in Polar Bear Game. Explore and survive a <strong>procedurally generated</strong>, <strong>infinite </strong>world, where, as a polar bear, you can choose whatever you want to do! <i>Who's going to stop you?</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293610/extras/b01aabf4c035cfeff05877d1496f7f34.avif?t=1676042637\" width=574 height=292 /></span><br><br>Gather resources and build your <strong>own</strong> house to keep your polar bear safe from the unknown dangers of the arctic night. Make sure you make a campfire before the sun sets, as the dark is deadly! Hunt enemies and bosses to <strong>level up</strong> your polar bear and make yourself stronger, you can find items in the world to either make the most tank polar bear imaginable or a glass cannon. The more days you survive, the harder the game gets, and the <strong>procedurally generated</strong> bosses are no different. How long will you survive?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293610/extras/005f1d87142c3a2facdf65722e4c55cd.avif?t=1676042637\" width=574 height=324 /></span><br><br>Polar Bear Game features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedurally generated infinite worlds</li><li>Building</li><li>Crafting</li><li>Procedurally generated bosses (could even be a chair!)</li><li>Increasing difficulty as you survive</li><li>Polar Bears!</li></ul>",
